n1, n2, .... ArrayPermute[array, {{perm1, n1}, {perm2, n2}, ...}] applies \
permk to level nk. ArrayPermute[array, {perm1, perm2, ...}] applies permk at \
the kth level. ArrayPermute[array, perm] or ArrayPermute[array, perm, All] is \
equivalent to ArrayPermute[array, perm, Range@ArrayDepth@array].", 
